        "Description": "Agent,\nHaven Island’s underground systems are more than a support network—they are the foundation of a covert initiative known as the Atlantis Protocol. A select group of individuals has been granted access to its inner workings, operating under the protection of Tyson Williams’ elite security detail.\n\nYou will assume that identity. Their uniform grants you proximity—but not forgiveness for mistakes.\n\nFive targets have been identified. Each plays a role in sustaining this hidden infrastructure. One of them remains below, embedded within the facility itself. Isolated. Unseen.\n\nEliminate all targets. The operative within the underground must be dealt with quietly—no noise, no trace. A fiber wire will suffice.\n\nPrecision over spectacle, 47.\nLet the city beneath the waves fall into silence.",
